## Memory System

> Persistent memory with Learning Loop — see docs/LEARNING-LOOP.md

### Available Commands

| Command | Action | Learning Loop Stage |
|---------|--------|---------------------|
| `/resume` | Pull + load last handoff | — |
| `/remember <slug>` | Save memory entry | 1. CAPTURE |
| `/recall <keyword>` | Search memory | 2. APPLY (pre) |
| `/apply <memory>` | Bump applied_count + announce | 2. APPLY |
| `/audit` | Session health report | 4. EVOLVE |
| `/promote <memory>` | Graduate to CLAUDE.md | 5. PROMOTE |
| `/handoff` | Audit + save + commit + push | 4. EVOLVE |

### Proactive Memory — AUTO

| Trigger | Action |
|---------|--------|
| New session start | Read `memory/latest-handoff.md` — summarize before starting |
| Important decision | `/remember` immediately — category: `decision` |
| Reusable pattern found | `/remember` immediately — category: `pattern` |
| Mistake or friction | `/remember` immediately — category: `lesson` |
| User says "remember this" | `/remember` immediately — category per content |
| End of session | `/handoff` immediately |
| Starting work on known topic | `/recall` first — check for existing context |

### Memory Storage

```
memory/
├── MEMORY.md                    <- Index (Map of Content)
├── _promotions.md               <- Promotion audit trail
├── _template/                   <- Memory file templates
│   ├── feedback-template.md
│   └── pattern-template.md
├── latest-handoff.md            <- Shortcut to latest handoff
└── YYYY-MM/                     <- Monthly folders
    └── YYYY-MM-DD-{type}-{slug}.md  <- Memory entries
```

